    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="基本数据结构"><a href="#基本数据结构" class="headerlink" title="基本数据结构"></a>基本数据结构</h2><p>js的基本数据类型（字节跳动）</p><p>String、Number、Null、undefined、Symbol、Boolean</p><p>Array、Map、Set</p><p>基本类型和引用类型是存放在哪里的</p><p>基本数据类型：堆</p><p>引用类型：栈</p><p>说说你对堆和栈的理解</p><p>代码输出题（给函数传入obj，修改某个属性，函数返回值是什么，obj的属性怎么变）</p><h2 id="闭包"><a href="#闭包" class="headerlink" title="闭包"></a>闭包</h2><p>闭包是什么</p><p>闭包的使用场景</p><p>闭包，因为我说闭包就是函数当类用，所以被问了二者的区别（米哈游）</p><h2 id="事件循环"><a href="#事件循环" class="headerlink" title="事件循环"></a>事件循环</h2><p>事件循环是什么</p><p>事件循环输出题</p><p>事件循环的应用是什么（答了vue的nexttick和react的setState）</p><h2 id="宏任务微任务"><a href="#宏任务微任务" class="headerlink" title="宏任务微任务"></a>宏任务微任务</h2><p>为什么setState要弄成微任务</p><p>promise——await底层原理，封装递归（米哈游）</p><h2 id="手写题："><a href="#手写题：" class="headerlink" title="手写题："></a>手写题：</h2><ul><li><p>手写一个链表要求有add和print方法，最后又写了个reverse方法（米哈游）</p></li><li><p>深拷贝</p></li><li><p>写题：每次输出下一个质数</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title function_">getNext</span>() <span class="comment">// 2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">getNext</span>() <span class="comment">// 3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">getNext</span>() <span class="comment">// 5</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>写题：EventEmitter</li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> e = <span class="title class_">EventEmitter</span>()</span><br><span class="line">e.<span class="title function_">on</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;foo&#x27;</span>, <span class="function">(<span class="params">name</span>) =&gt;</span> <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(name))</span><br><span class="line">e.<span class="title function_">emit</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;foo&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;bar&#x27;</span>) <span class="comment">// bar</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>实现 eventemitter，要求能在 on 的时候获取上次触发 emit 的事件（没太懂，只实现出基本的eventemiteer，玉玉了）</p></li><li><p>eventemitter中，once除了注册一个wrapper，wrapper中off。还有没有别的实现方法</p></li><li><p>setTimeout和setInterval的区别，输出顺序：（我答121212…刚才试了一下发现不对）</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">interval</span>(<span class="params"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">setTimeout</span>(<span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">interval</span>()</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;, <span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">interval</span>()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">setInterval</span>(<span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;, <span class="number">10</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>用它俩实现动画有什么区别？这两个到底有什么细微的区别？</p></li><li><p>实现动画：里面细节蛮多的，没搞好</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// TODO</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// fn(dom, styleKey, startVal, endVal, durationMS) 匀速变换方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 这是面试时候写的，之前没怎么练过，拉了</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">fn</span>(<span class="params">dom, styleKey, startVal, endVal, durationMS</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">let</span> step = <span class="title class_">Math</span>.<span class="title function_">ceil</span>((endVal - startVal) / <span class="number">16.6</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">helper</span>(<span class="params">dom, styleKey, startVal, end</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (end &gt;= endVal) <span class="keyword">return</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="title function_">requestAnimationFrame</span>(<span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            dom.<span class="property">style</span>.<span class="property">styleKey</span> = end</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="title function_">helper</span>(dom, styleKey, end, end + step)</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">helper</span>(dom, styleKey, startVal, startVal + step)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="场景题："><a href="#场景题：" class="headerlink" title="场景题："></a>场景题：</h2><ul><li><p>思考群聊和单聊的实现有什么不同（没做群聊）</p></li><li><p>已读功能怎么做的（intersectionObserver）</p></li><li><p>使用 intersectionObserver api 实现 useInView（自定义React hook，传入dom，判断该dom是否在显示区域内，返回true或false）不会做，又是拷打</p></li><li><p>描述 JSB 的实现</p></li><li><p>JSB 中有一个问题是连续发送多个请求会…怎么解决（没听懂问题，纯拷打）</p></li><li><p>字节里写好代码后如何让写的代码被用户看到（胡乱扯CI CD，还有…流水线）被提醒了CDN，又随便扯了一嘴</p></li><li><p>之前的代码会覆盖之后的代码吗，那回滚怎么做到的（我又说不是覆盖，但是不清楚这种更新策略怎么实现）</p></li></ul><h2 id="发展方向题"><a href="#发展方向题" class="headerlink" title="发展方向题"></a>发展方向题</h2><ul><li>之前为什么只实习了三个月，为什么接下来的一年都没继续实习（<strong>不敢说自己纠结过要不要留学</strong>）</li><li>为什么选择前端</li><li>职业规划（<strong>也没仔细想过，就说要先工作，后来想想是巨大减分项，教训之一</strong>）</li><li>觉得自己哪方面学的最不好（答的是算法，刷题能力一般，😨）</li><li>反问（<strong>可能是愣了，没有问出能体现我个人热情的问题</strong>），之后让我先退出去，其他两个人judge我，害怕</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
